This is a list of notable people reported as having died from coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19), as a result of infection by the virus SARS-CoV-2 during the ongoing COVID-19 pandemic.

Deaths[edit]

This is a dynamic list that may never be able to satisfy particular standards for completeness. You can help by adding missing persons provided: 1) a Wikipedia article exists about the person, and 2) COVID-19 has been reported as the cause of death in reliable sources (there is no need to include those sources here, but they must be present in each linked article.)
